gin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nSymbol\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Kain furing<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Cara 1 (Teknik Lem dengan\r\npanas setrika)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nSymbol\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Gunting bagian atas dan bawah\r\nkantong plastik, lalu gunting bagian pinggir, sehingga kantong plastik terbuka\r\nlebar.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nSymbol\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Lapisi bagian atas dan bawah\r\nkantong plastik dengan kertas baking.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nSymbol\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Setrika dengan suhu yang tidak\r\nterlalu panas dan tidak terlalu dingin. Sampai sini, lembaran kantong plastik\r\ndengan tekstur unik mirip kulit jeruk sudah didapat.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nSymbol\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Buat pola pouch atau tootebag\r\ndengan kardus. Jiplak pada lembaran plastik tadi, lalu gunting. Beri jarak pada\r\nbagian pinggir pouch yang akan direkatkan.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nSymbol\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Setrika kembali bagian pinggir\r\npouch hingga melekat sempurna dan pouch atau tootebag serbaguna siap dipakai.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Cara 2 (teknik jahit):<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nSymbol\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Caranya hampir sama dengan\r\nteknik lem dengan panas setrika, hanya saja pada bagiam dalam pouch atau\r\ntootebag dilapisi dengan kain furing, dan digunting sesuai pola.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nSymbol\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Setelah itu semua bagian\r\ndijahit dengan mesin jahit agar lebih rapi. Bisa juga dengan jahit tangan, cuma\r\nharus telaten kalau ingin hasilnya rapi.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\" calibri\",sans-serif;=\"\" mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:=\"\" minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:=\"\" en-us;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa\"=\"\"><br clear=\"all\" style=\"mso-special-character:line-break;\r\npage-break-before:always\"></span></p>', '2022-09-29 20:10:01');
