gin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;letter-spacing:.4pt;mso-font-kerning:\r\n     0pt;mso-ligatures:none;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID\">Bentuk\r\n     plastik dengan cetakan berbentuk bulat. Untuk tahapan ini, Moms dapat\r\n     menggunaka bekas&nbsp;<i>double tape,</i>&nbsp;ya.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 73); line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;letter-spacing:.4pt;mso-font-kerning:\r\n     0pt;mso-ligatures:none;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID\">Setelah\r\n     semua plastik sudah digunting berbentuk bulat, buat rawis dengan gunting\r\n     kecil. Pastikan potongannya jangan terlalu besar dan sisakan bagian\r\n     tengahnya<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 73); line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;letter-spacing:.4pt;mso-font-kerning:\r\n     0pt;mso-ligatures:none;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID\">Tusuk\r\n     bagian tengan plastik bekas menggunakan jarum. Lakukan langkah ini dengan\r\n     hati-hati, ya Moms.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 73); line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-po